Author: Roland Pfister [aut, cre], Solveig Tonn [aut], Moritz Schaaf [aut], 
    Robert Wirth [aut]
Maintainer: Roland Pfister <mail@roland-pfister.net>
Description: Tool helping psychologists and other behavioural scientists to
    analyze mouse movement (and other 2-D trajectory) data. Bundles together 
    several functions that compute spatial measures (MAD, AUC, sampen) or 
    provide a shorthand for often-used procedures.
